;li style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5rem; margin-block-end: 0.5rem;&quot; data-start-index=&quot;412&quot; class=&quot;paragraph list-item is-rich-chat-ui normal ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;&lt;b class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot; data-start-index=&quot;412&quot;&gt;功能&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot; data-start-index=&quot;414&quot;&gt;：將使用者的自然語言（例如：「幫我記下明天下午三點要開會」）傳送給 Gemini，並要求 AI 將其轉換為&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot; data-start-index=&quot;467&quot;&gt;結構化的 JSON 指令&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;&lt;button style=&quot;font: 500 11.008px / 16px &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;; letter-spacing: 0.096px; display: inline-flex; -webkit-box-pack: center; justify-content: center; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; vertical-align: middle; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-radius: 50%; padding: 0px; height: 1.375rem; width: 1.375rem; margin-inline-start: 0.25rem; cursor: pointer; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); color: rgb(94, 94, 94); transition: opacity 0.2s linear; opacity: 1; user-select: none;&quot; data-disabled=&quot;false&quot; aria-describedby=&quot;cdk-describedby-message-ng-1-26&quot; aria-haspopup=&quot;dialog&quot; class=&quot;xap-inline-dialog citation-marker ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;&lt;/button&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot; data-start-index=&quot;479&quot;&gt;。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.5rem; margin-block-end: 0.5rem;&quot; data-start-index=&quot;480&quot; class=&quot;paragraph list-item is-rich-chat-ui normal ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;&lt;b class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot; data-start-index=&quot;480&quot;&gt;運作邏輯&lt;/b&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot; data-start-index=&quot;484&quot;&gt;：它會定義 Prompt（提示詞），引導 AI 判斷使用者的意圖是「新增行程」、「查詢待辦」還是單純「閒聊」&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;&lt;button style=&quot;font: 500 11.008px / 16px &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;; letter-spacing: 0.096px; display: inline-flex; -webkit-box-pack: center; justify-content: center; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; vertical-align: middle; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-radius: 50%; padding: 0px; height: 1.375rem; width: 1.375rem; margin-inline-start: 0.25rem; cursor: pointer; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); color: rgb(94, 94, 94); transition: opacity 0.2s linear; opacity: 1; user-select: none;&quot; data-disabled=&quot;false&quot; aria-describedby=&quot;cdk-describedby-message-ng-1-26&quot; aria-haspopup=&quot;dialog&quot; class=&quot;xap-inline-dialog citation-marker ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;&lt;/button&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot; data-start-index=&quot;538&quot;&gt;。例如，它能將口語的「下週五」自動解析為具體的日期格式，以便後續存入資料庫&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ng-star-inserted&quot;&gt;&lt;button style=&quot;font: 500 11.008px / 16px &amp;quot;Google Sans Text&amp;quot;; letter-spacing: 0.096px; display: inline-flex; -webkit-box-pack: center; justify-content: center; -webkit-box-align: center; align-items: center; vertical-align: middle; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-radius: 50%; padding: 0px; height: 1.375rem; width: 1.375rem; margin-inline-start: 0.25rem; cursor: poin